c: 8
v: 34
t: "wkyf la ysthqqun eadhab allh, wahum yasuduwn 'awlia'ah almuminin ean altawaf balkebt walsalat fi almasjid alhram? wama kanuu 'awlia' allh, 'in 'awlia' allah 'iilaa aladhin ytqwnh bi'ada' fraydh wajtnab measyh, wlkn 'akthar alkufaar la yelmwn; fldhlk addaeu lanfshm amrana, ghyrhm 'uwlaa bh"